Welcome to East Grinstead

Annual Town Meeting

Notice is given of the ANNUAL TOWN MEETING to be held in the Meridian Hall, East Court, East Grinstead, on WEDNESDAY 20th March 2019 at 6 p.m. concluding at 7pm.

This is a public meeting, not a council meeting and is open to all members of the public to attend.

This will be a chance to meet with and gain a greater understanding of some of the volunteer and charitable organisations in the town. Tea and coffee will be available.

Welcome to East Grinstead Town Council’s web site. The site has three objectives. Firstly, it aims to inform about the role, organisation and decisions of the Town Council; secondly, to provide contact details and a timetable of meetings and thirdly to publish the latest news and comment about issues facing the Town and its Council.
